imdb.plot outline: Chileans who start new lives abroad, leaving behind an emotional bond with their country. These are the main characters of a new series about the Chilean diaspora. These adventurers do not rest until they achieve what was impossible in Chile, leaving their land, family and friends behind. Stories that open a window into the 21st century +shedding light into surprising corners of humanity.
